                  <interp inst="t18240407-9-crimeloc59" type="placeName" value="Poultry"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18240407-9-crimeloc59" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240407-9-off56 t18240407-9-crimeloc59"></join>, and felt a jerk at my pocket, and said my handkerchief was gone - I turned round and charged the prisoner with it; he was close behind - he denied it. I saw it in his hand, seized him, and saw him drop it. I took him to the Mansion House, and there he said that a boy had put it into his hand.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I told the Lord Mayor that I was walking along, saw it, and picked it up. The gentleman laid hold of me. I was so frightened I hardly knew what to say.</p>
